<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>We cannot answer calls from individuals about benefit or pension claims. Please <a href="https://www.gov.uk/contact-jobcentre-plus">contact Jobcentre Plus</a> or <a href="https://www.gov.uk/contact-pension-service">contact The Pension Service</a> instead.</p>

<h2 id="national-media-and-london-area-enquiries-only">National media and London area enquiries only</h2>
<p>For national media and London area enquiries only, call our London Press Office on 020 3267 5144.</p>

<h2 id="england-and-wales-local-media-enquiries">England and Wales local media enquiries</h2>
<p>For England and Wales local media enquiries, call 029 20 586 then 097 or 098 or 099.</p>

<h2 id="scotland-local-media-enquiries">Scotland local media enquiries</h2>
<p>For Scotland local media enquiries, call 01506 772 688.</p>

<h2 id="opening-hours">Opening hours</h2>
<p>We are open Monday to Friday, 9am to 6pm.</p>

<p>Outside these hours, call 07623 928 975 (journalists only).</p>

